      <title>波兰金融监管机构为Erste收购桑坦德银行开绿灯</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/polish-financial-regulator-gives-green-light-erstes-takeover-santander-2025-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰金融监管机构 (KNF) 周三在一份声明中表示，已批准 Erste Group Bank AG 收购波兰桑坦德银行控股权。]]></description>
