      <title>美联储沃勒表示他“绝对”会捍卫美联储的独立性</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/feds-waller-says-he-absolutely-would-defend-us-central-banks-independence-2025-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒(Christopher Waller)是明年接替美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)的候选名单之一，他周三表示，如果美联储的独立性受到美国总统的挑战，他将“绝对”捍卫美联储的独立性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/feds-waller-says-he-absolutely-would-defend-us-central-banks-independence-2025-12-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Dec 2025 16:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
