      <title>贝莱德和投资者达里奥为“特朗普账户”提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/investor-ray-dalio-help-fund-trump-accounts-some-children-2025-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，亿万富翁投资者雷·达利奥(Ray Dalio)将帮助特朗普政府为康涅狄格州某些儿童的投资账户提供资金，而另一家公司也誓言将匹配员工的捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/investor-ray-dalio-help-fund-trump-accounts-some-children-2025-12-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Dec 2025 15:35:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
